description:
"TALES FROM THE VOID - VOLUME THREE"

An unofficial Warhammer horror anthology.

Three community written tales set within the worlds of Warhammer, chosen by a group of judges on the official discord channel during the Halloween writing competition.

Narrated and produced by A Vox in the Void.

"THE HOLLOW ROT" - BY LIAM SELL (Warhammer 40k)
Featuring music by @DreamClinicOfficial 

"A RATIONAL MIND" - BY SAGGIO MIK (Warhammer fantasy)
Featuring music from epidemic sound

"MEAT HOOKS" - BY SEVERN DAY (Necromunda)
featuring music by @myersmusicofficial 

Join the discord for more competitions and community writing!

https://discord.gg/9wTS7nkUpA

Check out the official merch store!

https://avoxinthevoid.creator-spring.com/

#warhammer #avoxinthevoid #horrorstories
title: "TALES FROM THE VOID - VOLUME III" - A WARHAMMER HORROR ANTHOLOGY
